      "cookedHtml": "<p>Whether you’re in marketing, gamedev, or consulting, client feedback cycles often stretch approvals and delay project delivery​<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/hourglass_not_done.png?v=15\" title=\":hourglass_not_done:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":hourglass_not_done:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />.</p>\n<p>Why?<br />\nYour client isn’t really part of the workflow. So you send Gantt PDFs, chase feedback, and wait for replies.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/worried.png?v=15\" title=\":worried:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":worried:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />More PDF versions.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/worried.png?v=15\" title=\":worried:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":worried:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />More follow-ups.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/worried.png?v=15\" title=\":worried:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":worried:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />But still delays in testing and launching…</p>\n<p>With Interactive Gantt Timeline, you can 𝗰𝗼𝗹𝗹𝗮𝗯𝗼𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗲 𝗱𝗶𝗿𝗲𝗰𝘁𝗹𝘆 𝘄𝗶𝘁𝗵 𝗰𝗹𝗶𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝗼𝗻 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗚𝗮𝗻𝘁𝘁.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=15\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />Clients comment and suggest timeline shifts in context.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/test_tube.png?v=15\" title=\":test_tube:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":test_tube:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> You, as a PM, test scenarios before applying them.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/counterclockwise_arrows_button.png?v=15\" title=\":counterclockwise_arrows_button:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":counterclockwise_arrows_button:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Approved changes sync automatically to your monday board.</p>\n<p>One 𝗹𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗚𝗮𝗻𝘁𝘁 instead of endless PDFs.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/f/bf1485d82fc8665494b757e642af6cddf874ad90.png\" title=\"1323\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/f/bf1485d82fc8665494b757e642af6cddf874ad90_2_690x345.png\" alt=\"1323\" width=\"690\" height=\"345\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">1323</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 243 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/c/acaabbbda2c143b1258803111afa683e4bdffd1c.gif\" alt=\"Interactive Gantt (1)\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\" class=\"animated\" /></p>\n<p>Try this approach and see the difference​<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10001052/interactive-gantt-timeline\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10001052/interactive-gantt-timeline</a></p>"
